OL,3,CHuge 'house party' planned for Ricky
OL,4,CHatton at Manchester's AO Arena
OL,6,FHero boxing champ Ricky Hatton will be
OL,7,Fremembered with a night labelled a
OL,8,F"huge house party" at the arena where
OL,9,Fhe thrilled fight fans.
OL,11,FHis son Campbell has joined close
OL,12,Ffriend and fellow boxer Anthony Crolla
OL,13,Fto invite fans to join in with the
OL,14,Fnight on 7 June at the AO Arena, in
OL,15,FManchester.
OL,17,FIt will see acts from the world of
OL,18,Fsport, comedy and music performing to
OL,19,Fraise money for mental health
OL,20,Fcharities.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
