OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777021560
OL,3,CHuge 'house party' planned for Ricky
OL,4,CHatton at Manchester's AO Arena
OL,6,FThe 46 year old was found dead at his
OL,7,Fhome in Gee Cross in Hyde in September
OL,8,F2025.
OL,10,FRicky Hatton had openly spoken about
OL,11,Fhis struggles with his mental health.
OL,12,FAt an inquest in March 2026 a coroner
OL,13,Fruled he could not be satisfied that
OL,14,Fthe boxer had intended to take his own
OL,15,Flife.
OL,17,FHis son says his dad's honesty has
OL,18,Fhelped others seek help.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777021560
OL,3,CHuge 'house party' planned for Ricky
OL,4,CHatton at Manchester's AO Arena
OL,6,F"I think we've come a long way from
OL,7,Fwhere we were years ago, but I think
OL,8,Fit's one thing knowing you have to
OL,9,Ftalk and doing it," Campbell said.
OL,11,F"I think events like this, with people
OL,12,Fin the public eye, will give people a
OL,13,Fbit more confidence to go and do it."
OL,15,FStars of the boxing world will take
OL,16,Fpart from Frank Bruno to Natasha
OL,17,FJonas, the stage will be a boxing ring
OL,18,Fin the centre of the arena where Ricky
OL,19,FHatton fights thrilled fans for years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
