FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777021560
OL,3,CHuge 'house party' planned for Ricky
OL,4,CHatton at Manchester's AO Arena
OL,6,FHe was a true blue Manchester City fan
OL,7,Fbut often brought together fans from
OL,8,FManchester United and Paul Scholes is
OL,9,Fone of the sports legends who'll be
OL,10,Fthere on the night.
OL,12,FAnthony Crolla says it will be a
OL,13,Fchance, after the tragedy of his
OL,14,Fdeath, to remember the hitman with a
OL,15,Fsmile.
OL,17,F"I often think of this place as
OL,18,FRicky's house and in a way it'll be a
OL,19,Fhouse party," he says.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
