PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777021560
OL,3,CHuge 'house party' planned for Ricky
OL,4,CHatton at Manchester's AO Arena
OL,6,FBackstage at the arena there is now a
OL,7,FRicky Hatton suite in honour of the
OL,8,Fmuch-loved boxer. It features a blue
OL,9,Fplaque to his memory and pictures of
OL,10,Fhis great moments in the ring.
OL,12,FThe plaque marks his fifteen fights
OL,13,Fthere and his legendary victory over
OL,14,FKostya Tszyu in June 2005.
OL,16,FAs Campbell Hatton describes the
OL,17,Fforthcoming event, "Dad would love to
OL,18,Fbe there".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
